reviewText: I bought this boxset only because I wanted to see the first one. But the single DVD of the first (and probably only great) "Beethoven" is full screen. This boxset has "Beethoven" (and its four sequels) in its original widescreen format. This DVD set has all 5 movies spread out over two discs.
summary: Not all the movies are great but it's the best version to buy
